OL,3,CThousands gather to remember stabbing
OL,4,Cvictim
OL,6,FITV Meridian's Mike Pearse reports
OL,7,Ffrom Reading. He spoke to Mian Saleem
OL,8,Ffrom the Reading Pakistani centre,
OL,9,FCllr Amjad Tarar, Lab, from Reading
OL,10,FBorough Council and MP Matt Rodda.
OL,12,FMourners have gathered for the funeral
OL,13,Fof a 20 year old man from Reading who
OL,14,Fdied after being stabbed.
OL,16,FMore than 2000 people said prayers at
OL,17,FKings Meadow Park during a multi-faith
OL,18,Fcelebration in memory of Muhammed Noor
OL,19,FMajid Butt, known as Noor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
