OL,3,CThousands gather to remember stabbing
OL,4,Cvictim
OL,6,FFamily, friends and members of the
OL,7,Flocal community came together to
OL,8,Fremember the young man, who died
OL,9,Ffollowing the incident in Lower Earley
OL,10,Fon 23rd of May.
OL,12,FOfficers attended alongside other
OL,13,Fmedical professionals, but Noor died
OL,14,Flater in hospital.
OL,16,FMP Matt Rodda joined mourners saying:
OL,17,F"This shows the community coming
OL,18,Ftogether after an unspeakable tragedy.
OL,20,F"People have been wonderful in showing
OL,21,Ftheir support."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
