OL,3,CThousands gather to remember stabbing
OL,4,Cvictim
OL,6,FNoor's family also paid tribute,
OL,7,Fdescribing him as a "kind, loving
OL,8,Fsoul".
OL,10,FThey said: "Our family is heartbroken
OL,11,Fby the loss of our beloved son.
OL,13,F"He was a kind, loving soul who always
OL,14,Fput others before himself and touched
OL,15,Fthe lives of so many with his
OL,16,Fcompassion and warmth."
OL,18,FA 16-year-old boy from Reading has
OL,19,Fbeen charged with one count each of
OL,20,Fmurder and possession of an offensive
OL,21,Fweapon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
